194
00:10:39,021 --> 00:10:40,421
Jari?

195
00:10:40,421 --> 00:10:42,421
Di cermin biasa, akan ada celah

196
00:10:42,421 --> 00:10:44,421
antara jarimu dan pantulannya,

197
00:10:44,421 --> 00:10:50,121
