200
00:10:53,521 --> 00:10:55,021
gambar asli dan gambar di cermin

201
00:10:55,021 --> 00:10:57,621
tampak seolah melekat menjadi satu!

202
00:10:57,621 --> 00:11:00,721
Ketika kita menyalakan lampu dari sisi ini,

203
00:11:00,721 --> 00:11:03,421
