204
00:11:03,421 --> 00:11:05,421
Semua pakaian yang digantung?

205
00:11:05,421 --> 00:11:07,721
Aku mengerti!

206
00:11:07,721 --> 00:11:09,721
Lemari ruangan sebelah!

