muncul di cermin selesai.

216
00:11:33,721 --> 00:11:35,721
Jadi, sekarang kau tahu.

217
00:11:35,721 --> 00:11:38,621
Sang pelaku secara putus asa menggunakan trik

218
00:11:38,621 --> 00:11:41,121
